form(id="RequestFrom", action="").request-form.mercedes-daimlercac-regular-font
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
        .form-group.validate
            label(for="name").field-title Name*
            input(type="text" name="name" required).form-control
            span.field-error
                i.warning-icon
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding
            .form-group.validate
                label(for="phone").field-title Phone*
                input(type="text" name="phone" required minlength="12" maxlength="15").form-control
                span.field-error
                    i.warning-icon

        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8.col-lg-8.row-no-padding
            .form-group.group-right.validate
                label(for="email").field-title Email*
                input(type="text" name="email" required).form-control
                span.field-error
                    i.warning-icon
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding
        .form-group
            label(for="method").field-title Preferred Contact Method/Time
            input(type="text" name="method").form-control
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8.col-lg-8.row-no-padding
        .interest-in.group-right.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
            p.field-title Interested In
            .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding-left
                .form-group
                    .checkbox
                        input(type="checkbox" name="aClass" id="aClass").form-control
                        label(for="aClass") A-Class
            .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-4.col-lg-4.center
                .form-group
                    .checkbox
                        input(type="checkbox" name="claCouple" id="claCouple").form-control
                        label(for="claCouple") CLA Coupe
            .col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-4.col-lg-4.last
                .form-group
                    .checkbox
                        input(type="checkbox" name="others" id="others").form-control
                        label(for="others") Others
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding
        .form-group
            label(for="vehicle").field-title.label-custom Vehicle Interest
            input(type="text" name="vehicle").form-control
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-8.col-lg-8.row-no-padding
        .form-group.group-right
            label(for="enquiry").field-title.label-custom Enquiry
            input(type="text" name="enquiry").form-control
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
        .privacy
            p.field-title Privacy
            div
                span At Mercedes-Benz Financial Services Singapore, a part of the Daimler Group, we share your concerns regarding privacy and data security. When you provide us with your personal information, we will only disclose such information within the Daimler Group of Companies, your authorised dealer network and/or service providers who are acting on our behalf. You can either view our privacy statement <span><a href="#" class="link link-here">here</a></span> or by contacting our Privacy Officer at <a class="mail mailto" href="mailto:mbfs_sg@daimler.com">mbfs_sg@daimler.com </a>
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
        .communication
            p.field-title Future Communications
            div
                span In addition to the purpose of my enquiry, I provide my consent for MBFS, a part of the Daimler Group, our authorised dealer network and/or third party service providers to contact me for direct marketing purposes, including but not limited to newsletters, event notifications, invitations, updates and special offers from time to time. In relation to this, please communicate with me via:
            .communication-type.col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-7.col-lg-7.row-no-padding
                .col-xs-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding.group.first
                    .form-group
                        .checkbox
                            input(type="checkbox" name="via-phone" id="via-phone").form-control
                            label(for="via-phone") Phone
                .col-xs-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding.group.center
                    .form-group
                        .checkbox
                            input(type="checkbox" name="via-email" id="via-email").form-control
                            label(for="via-email") Email
                .col-xs-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.col-lg-4.row-no-padding.last
                    .form-group
                        .checkbox
                            input(type="checkbox" name="via-sms" id="via-sms").form-control
                            label(for="via-sms") SMS/MMS/IM
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding
        .message-plugin
            p Enter message as shown
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-6.col-lg-6.row-no-padding
                .message-content.mercedes-daimlercs-light-font
                    span.text space for security plugin
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.row-no-padding.btn-group
        button.cta-btn(title='Submit')
            p Submit
                i.icon.chevron-left